    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still running like a dream! It\u2019s in great shape, well-loved, and ready for all your upcoming road trips. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that won't let you down, this is the one. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
