    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! It runs smooth as silk and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures. If you're looking for a reliable, comfy car that still looks sharp in the driveway, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
