      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp gear engagement, feeding power through the factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a subframe reinforcement already completed\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the compression remains within spec across all cylinders. It sits on staggered 19-inch Style 67 wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, ensuring optimal lateral grip and precise turn-in response.",
